<p>In Meteor template <code>{{parameter}}</code> returns value of option for this schema:</p>  <pre><code>new SimpleSchema({   parameter: {     type: String,     allowedValues: ['value_1', 'value_2'],     autoform: {       options: [         {label: "label_1", value: 'value_1'},         {label: "label_2", value: 'value_2'}       ]     }   }, }); </code></pre>  <p>How can I get <code>label</code> instead of <code>value</code> in my template?</p>